# Potato Vegetable Soup

Based on [https://cooking.nytimes.com/recipes/1025764-potato-leek-soup](https://cooking.nytimes.com/recipes/1025764-potato-leek-soup) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251117233518/https://cooking.nytimes.com/recipes/1025764-potato-leek-soup))

